" VIMRC, options for default VIM use

set nocompatible "Use Vim settings rather than Vi settings

set backspace=indent,eol,start "Allow backspacing over everything in insert mode

set autoindent "Turn on auto-indenting 

set tabstop=4 "A tab is denoted as four spaces

set shiftwidth=4 "Use 4 spaces in indents in autoindent

set autoindent "Always set auto indenting on

set textwidth=80

set selectmode=mouse "Select when using the mouse

set ruler "Show the cursor position at all times

set showmatch "Show the matching bracket for ')' etc

set number "shows line numbers

set wrapscan "lets search wrap to top of document




